data.description: This charming 2-bed, 2.5-bath townhome, located in Central Point, close to schools, parks, shopping, & dining. With vaulted ceilings, two comfortable living areas, and a bright and light kitchen, this property is the epitome of modern living. The main floor boasts a versatile office space at the front - perfect for remote work or a cozy reading nook and the shared wall has additional sound proofing to complete the peace. The open-concept living area creates a warm and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring modern appliances, ample counter space, and a breakfast bar. Upstairs, the two generous bedrooms offer comfort & privacy, while the vaulted ceilings create an airy, spacious feel. Both bedrooms have their own en-suite baths, adding a touch of luxury to your daily routine. The laundry room is located on the top floor near the bedrooms for your convenience. The attached garage allows for plenty of space for storage and parking.
